  "text": "Ref. [CITATION_1] , an algorithm for incremental neural network construction that is capable of learning new information without forgetting the old knowledge is proposed. This algorithm is based on the combination of RBF modules and fuzzy systems. An incremental training method for the probabilistic RBF is presented in Ref. [CITATION_2] .",
